727086f-b.text:
Jamaica Avenue, at the S.E. corner of 214th Street, showing a house in a set of two views, belonging to J. G. Hendrickson from 1873-1891.  Other owners were J. Vanderveer and J Van Degrew. Note the new type house in view 3.
View 1: May 1923
View 2: April 1926
View 3: March 4, 1927
Eugene L Armbruster Collection
View 3: P L Sperr
